text: Churayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Meneuztamaksky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 130 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 4 km from Meneuztamak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Churayevo, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
